    <string name="large_text">
        * <b>Help</b>\n\n

        Caller Announce is a free and open source Android App that announces the name or phone
        number of the caller.\n
        Tap the talk bubble icon to start announcing caller names and numbers.\n
        Tap it again to stop announcements when you need to, such as when you are in a meeting.\n\n

        Tap the Settings button for adding some spice.\n
        Set your name to blank if you prefer.\n\n

